Introduction

Class Calculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • Introduction.Calculator

  • public class Calculator
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will take two inputs as parameters and will contain methods to perform some of the most basic calculations that are available using a calculator.
    Version:
    1.22.2020
    Author:
    Matthew Grillo mwgrillo
